    All nontrivial zeros of the Riemann zeta function lie in this strip.

    This is a fundamental region for studying the behavior of the zeta function,
    particularly regarding its zeros. -/
def CriticalStrip : Set ℂ :=
  {s : ℂ | 0 < s.re ∧ s.re < 1}

